{"data":[{"date":"23:35 08/08","title":"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CHINH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khi chia tay logo c\u0169 sang th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu m\u1edbi mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean Serie A nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129. L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh khi Serie A h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Premier League v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1c CLB b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo nh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Serie A c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c g\u00f3i ba n\u0103m gi\u1ed1ng Premier League. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo m\u1edbi theo h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o ch\u1eef \"A\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Serie A c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Facebook, Instagram v\u00e0 Twitter, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u00ean \"SerieA\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng h\u01a1n h\u01a1n 1.2 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Serie A t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \"xu\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1\". Ch\u1eef A trong logo m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \"Appassionante, Avvincente, Adrenalinica\" - t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch \"th\u00fa v\u1ecb, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u01a1m Adrenaline\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Logo cu cua Serie A.\" title=\"Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/serie-a-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng logo m\u1edbi b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \"khao kh\u00e1t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ednh trung t\u00e2m cho ch\u1eef A\", c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \"m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\". Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo Serie A c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Italia nh\u01b0 Coppa Italia, Si\u00eau C\u00fap Italia v\u00e0 Primavera.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c quan, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m l\u00e1 c\u1edd Italia, m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u1eef A, t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi TIM\" - Tr\u00edch t\u1eeb th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Serie A 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a-176-193919.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-khi-sao-serie-a-la-mieng-pizza-trong-mat-cac-dai-gia-nha-172-192560.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Khi sao Serie A l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng pizza trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube-188-192551.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5261","checkdouble":"194058"},{"date":"22:54 08/08","title":"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/loai-van-lam-hlv-park-hang-seo-da-noi-gi-voi-thu-mon-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y?\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park b\u1edfi \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng 3 su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i U23 cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mang t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn cho ch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 mong V\u0103n L\u00e2m th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi an \u1ee7i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 di\u1ec5n ra trong 10 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung xoay quanh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn ai, b\u1ecf ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m khi \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb \u00f4ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft b\u1edfi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201cqu\u00e1 m\u1ecfng\u201d. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ebfn AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay, khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa, V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u01a1i b\u1edbt n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay khi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 AFF Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u00e0o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00ed h\u1eadu, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Indonesia. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi bi\u1ebft tin b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dang-van-lam-bi-loai-bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-472-193976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dang-van-lam-bi-loai-bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-472-193976.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Asiad 2018: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u00eat Nam \u2013 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5260","checkdouble":"194057"},{"date":"00:37 09/08","title":"Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Tien-ve-Minh-Vuong-noi-mot-dieu-sau-khi-bi-loai-khoi-DT-Olympic-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i do anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman v\u1eeba qua. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 anh h\u00e0o, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sa khi bi\u1ebft tin m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n, song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \"C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m cho t\u00f4i. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. Xin ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\". <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 qu\u00ea Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i U23. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Xem ch\u1eebng Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 khi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh tham gia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5259","checkdouble":"194060"},{"date":"20:21 08/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: \"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh\", BLV Quang Huy nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Arsenal, Jens Lehmann nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Arsene Wenger, HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 88 Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 88 Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Diem-tin-toi-88-Man-Utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Rooney nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wayne Rooney kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Real Madrid \u0111ang d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Luka Modric. Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia loan tin Inter \u0111ang t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Kim Hak-bum c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock out, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olivier Giroud ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Fekir ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lyon v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Moussa Wague v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 13 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Senegal v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u00e2u Phi ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi quan c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos, Dani Ceballos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo ra \u0111i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Viec Van Quyet du ASIAD 2018 gay nhieu tranh cai.\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/IMG_1147.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wolverhampton \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Adama Traore t\u1eeb Middlesbrough v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Wolverhampton m\u1edbi l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Everton trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), s\u1edbm h\u01a1n ba tu\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u1ee3i l\u00ean ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB khi\u1ebfn G\u0110\u0110H Premier League, Richard Scudamore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed1i 8/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-tottenham-truoc-mua-giai-201819-nguy-co-vang-khoi-top-4-172-194053.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: Nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi Top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\">N\u00f3ng: Athletic Bilbao x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Kepa Arrizabalaga s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lo-dau-hieu-cho-thay-kovacic-sap-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194048.html\">L\u1ed9 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Kovacic s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kepa-arrizabalaga-co-du-kha-nang-thay-the-vi-tri-do-courtois-de-lai-172-194047.html\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/jose-mourinho-va-manchester-united-mua-bong-moi-ao-mong-cuoi-cung-392-194046.html\">Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Manchester United m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi: \u1ea2o m\u1ed9ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5258","checkdouble":"194054"},{"date":"05:53 09/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8: Chelsea l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-98-chelsea-lap-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 9/8.</h2><h2>Everton l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Barca hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Andre Gomes. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Andre Gomes thay v\u00ec mua \u0111\u1ee9t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa\" title=\"Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng 9/8: Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Courtois. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 The Blues ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Athletic Bilbao l\u00e0 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u1ee9c kho\u1ea3ng 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kepa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp c\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Schalke ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn sao Tottenham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Rose \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Schalke thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 Bundesliga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 31/8 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho Schalke trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Spurs.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Boateng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Jose Mourinho mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giao k\u00e8o mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Man United b\u1ecb h\u1edb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Vida</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Evening Standard cho bi\u1ebft Arsenal \u0111ang quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Danny Welbeck t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Besiktas ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia. Vida \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-184-194054.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-184-193992.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5257","checkdouble":"194063"},{"date":"22:48 08/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/barcelona-chieu-mo-moussa-wague.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Moussa Wague, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u00e2u Phi t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</h2><h2>Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Moussa Wague<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Moussa Wague, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Barca sau Arthur Mele, Clement Lenglet, Malcom v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Moussa Wague h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Moussa Wague h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/barcelona-chieu-mo-moussa-wague.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Moussa Wague v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMoussa Wague \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 3/8, c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu trong h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i, Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 4.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho CLB KAS Eupen (B\u1ec9).\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia c\u0169ng th\u00f2ng v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Moussa Wague s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Moussa Wague tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Barca B.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Moussa Wague l\u00e0 ai?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7 Aspire (Qatar), Moussa Wague n\u0103m nay 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. Tuy c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Wague \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ec9, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Europa League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Eupen v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn sau hai m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wague \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i sau khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Wague tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u Phi tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0110T Senegal ph\u1ea3i chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Wague \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi 13 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Senegal.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barcelona h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal-184-194031.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-kha-nang-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-dembele-172-193917.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/nong-paul-pogba-dat-thoa-thuan-voi-barca-187-193906.html\">N\u00f3ng: Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina-172-193764.html\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal-180-193703.html\">Barca c\u00f3 Vidal, Valverde vui nh\u01b0 \u201cm\u1edf c\u1edd trong b\u1ee5ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\">Ch\u00ea Alderweireld v\u00e0 Maguire qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, M.U ch\u1ed1t mua ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5256","checkdouble":"194056"},{"date":"06:11 09/08","title":"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dirk Kuyt kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Lovren \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Kuyt \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Lovren</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Lovren trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1ea1i Anfield. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, Lovren c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat-421-191045.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/lovren-nhm-ung-ho-toi-nhieu-hon-modric-va-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Lovren s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/dejan-lovren-44909.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lovren</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLovren l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch khi xem Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 gi\u00e2y. Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Croatia r\u1ed3i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Kuyt d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Liverpool s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kuyt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Feyenoord gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 Kuyt tin r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Liverpool ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t Premier League khi \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi Feyenoord, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u sau 18 n\u0103m. T\u00f4i tin Liverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sau 29 n\u0103m v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Van Dijk s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-co-bong-dang-cua-nha-vo-dich-sau-khi-chieu-mo-alisson-172-194000.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-thua-nhan-liverpool-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong-172-193996.html\">Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Liverpool ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5255","checkdouble":"194064"},{"date":"06:33 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>Kepa gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 7 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 71.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kepa t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kepa \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge</span> \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 Premier League. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Chelsea n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Kepa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge khi Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kepa ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu sao, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Caballero \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Marina Granovskaia kh\u00e1 h\u00e2n hoan v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKepa l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00edch khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kepa \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba k\u00fd v\u1edbi Kepa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5254","checkdouble":"194065"},{"date":"06:33 09/08","title":"Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid nh\u01b0 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\nTr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 CLB, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid l\u1eabn Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng nay theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u0169ng s\u1ebd sang Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ngay sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois xong xu\u00f4i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ed1i nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Thibaut Courtois sau khi th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Sau khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, Mateo Kovacic s\u1ebd sang The Blues theo d\u1ea1ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\", Chelsea th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cReal Madrid C.F v\u00e0 Chelsea F.C \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00ed h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB 6 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1 gi\u1edd chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 9/8 \u1edf SV\u0110 Santiago Bernabeu\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid sau khi r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid sau khi r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Thu-mon-Courtois-chinh-thuc-den-Real-Madrid-sau-khi-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1ecfa \u01b0\u1edbc nguy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n\" 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u00fd r\u1eddi The Blues, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \"n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n\" n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Courtois khi\u1ebfn anh nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf  h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kepa Arrizabalaga t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf ra 72  tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Kepa v\u1ec1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, qua \u0111\u00f3  gi\u00fap anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t Alisson Becker (Liverpool) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t  th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Genk v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ea3i qua 3 m\u00f9a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp (2011-2014) thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Atletico Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. T\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2014-15, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 The Blues thay Petr Cech (sang Arsenal), ra s\u00e2n 154 tr\u1eadn, gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 1 FA Cup c\u00f9ng 1 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n.\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00e8 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lo-dau-hieu-cho-thay-kovacic-sap-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194048.html\">L\u1ed9 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Kovacic s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kepa-arrizabalaga-co-du-kha-nang-thay-the-vi-tri-do-courtois-de-lai-172-194047.html\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5253","checkdouble":"194067"},{"date":"06:53 09/08","title":"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/loay-hoay-tim-trung-ve-mourinho-tinh-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm Zouma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Man United ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Zouma \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c. B\u1edfi The Blues kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd c\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZouma kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Stoke. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi The Potters \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Zouma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Loay hoay t\u00ecm trung v\u1ec7, Mourinho t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Zouma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/loay-hoay-tim-trung-ve-mourinho-tinh-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kurt Zouma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a Zouma v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea n\u0103m 2014. V\u00e0 t\u1edd L\u2019Equipe \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, MU s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Everton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zouma theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea t\u1eebng b\u00e1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho Man United. Mourinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea9y Mata \u0111\u1ebfn Man United n\u0103m 2014 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Nemanja Matic c\u0169ng m\u1edbi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Mourinho \u1edf United h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c mua trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Zouma ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn sau khi Man United kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld v\u00e0 Harry Maguire nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng do ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. Jerome Boateng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay. V\u00e0 Man United ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw-172-194037.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5252","checkdouble":"194068"},{"date":"06:55 09/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League h\u00e8 2018 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda (9/8)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/chuyen-nhuong-premier-league-ngay-dong-cua.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League h\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (9/8). Cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda TTCN Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00e8 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>* Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premir League h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</strong><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois m\u00e0 Real Madrid m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real v\u1eabn coi Kovacic l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, Luka Modric \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic gia nh\u1eadp Real v\u00e0o h\u00e8 2015 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kho\u1ea3ng 29 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u00f3 109 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 &ldquo;k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5&rdquo; v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i sau khi World Cup kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic se khoac ao Chelsea mua 2018-19\" title=\"Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea m\u00f9a 2018-19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/180809_054945_649.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovacic s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea m\u00f9a 2018-19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG QUAN TTCN PREMIER LEAGUE NG\u00c0Y \u0110\u00d3NG C\u1eecA</h2>\r\nN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8. Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 31/8 nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng l\u1ec7 th\u00ec b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi sau ng\u00e0y 9/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a tu\u1ea7n khai m\u1ea1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 23h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c CLB v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (mua ho\u1eb7c m\u01b0\u1ee3n) n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edf c\u1eeda l\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y 1/1/2019. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 sau ng\u00e0y 9/8 v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00ec thu\u1ed9c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a UEFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 trong n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 Premier League. C\u00e1c CLB v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sang c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 31/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5251","checkdouble":"194069"},{"date":"15:25 08/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nguoi-dep-co-phat-ngon-gay-soc-la-ban-gai-moi-cua-tien-ve-trong-dai.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5250","checkdouble":"194035"},{"date":"17:32 08/08","title":"B\u00e0o ch\u1eefa v\u1ee5 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Conte, Willian tr\u00e1ch con g\u00e1i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/bao-chua-vu-coi-thuong-thay-cu-conte-willian-trach-con-gai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea, Willian \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e1ch c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i y\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 HLV Conte.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man United gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup 2017/18, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea, Willian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh The Blues n\u00e2ng C\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh HLV Conte b\u1ecb che k\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eb1ng 3 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u00fap V\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Conte c\u1ee7a Willian.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/NINTCHDBPICT000425311293_2018080810242517.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean ESPN Brasil v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5y C\u00fap che m\u1eb7t Conte trong b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao Brazil cho hay, ch\u00ednh c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i y\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCon g\u00e1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 g\u1eafn nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay v\u1ec1 Brazil. Khi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 (Conte b\u1ecb che m\u1eb7t) v\u00ec qu\u00e1 m\u1ec7t\u201d, Willian cho hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u201ctai n\u1ea1n\u201d n\u00f3i tr\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Willian m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u00f4ng khai b\u00e0y t\u1ecf b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Conte, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Willian c\u00f4ng k\u00edch Conte \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0nh x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, khi\u1ebfn The Blues m\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat quan tr\u1ecdng Diego Costa.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5249","checkdouble":"194041"}]}